<h2 class="contentheading">
	Add To My Yahoo Module and Tutorial</h2>








Do you syndicate your site using RSS? If so, install the Add to My Yahoo! module. This allows your visitors to add your article headlines to their My Yahoo! start pages, without having to configure a newsreader.
<p>
	<a href="tutorials/23-add-to-my-yahoo-module-and-tutorial" class="readon">
		Read more: Add To My Yahoo Module and Tutorial</a>
</p>

		</div>
